The paper focuses on improving the quality of generated images using human annotations, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep neural networks to predict the attributes also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The statistical analysis of the annotated dataset may also fall under the category of graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
